text.tspan: * Using nanometer process has two drawbacks:
* PDK very complex to do it by ourselves, better
use a process which the EDA has a PDK already
* Extraction tools are very complex, not available
* Some testbenches examples should be done prior
to the designer start to do his job.
* More exploration needed on doing veriloga testbenches
* Other new veriloga models available using mot-verilog
* Gnucap used for transient, AC, Fourier and OP analisys.
* If other analisys is needed, LTSpice is available too
* Prepare a set of python scripts at the
EDA setup stage, to easy designer
scripts with minor modifications if any
